## Test Case ID: TC-CRM-001
Title: Verify that Recruitment Strategy Template content is correctly inserted
Related Ticket: CRM-2437
Preconditions: User must be logged in as RCM Recruitment user
## Steps:
  1. Navigate to ActivityMobile
  2. Click into the 'Recruitment Strategy' field
  3. Select a template from the template list
  4. Click on 'Insert Template'
## Expected Result:
  - The text box should populate with the template data
  - Previous data should not be overwritten if present
